t" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Tutto nell&#x27;EHR</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Ogni registrazione dei tracciatori è archiviata nella cartella del paziente — nessun silo.</p></div><div class="text-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-success/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-8 w-8 text-green-success" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Collega Dispositivi e App</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">I pazienti si sincronizzano da Apple Health, Google Health Connect o dispositivi.</p></div><div class="text-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target h-8 w-8 text-purple-accent" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Alimenta i Piani di Assistenza RPM</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">I dati dei tracciatori alimentano soglie personalizzate, avvisi e monitoraggio.</p></div><div class="text-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-startup/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-brain h-8 w-8 text-orange-startup" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 18V5"></path><path d="M15 13a4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3-4 4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3 4"></path><path d="M17.598 6.5A3 3 0 1 0 12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.598 1.5"></path><path d="M17.997 5.125a4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77"></path><path d="M18 18a4 4 0 0 0 2-7.464"></path><path d="M19.967 17.483A4 4 0 1 1 12 18a4 4 0 1 1-7.967-.517"></path><path d="M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-2-7.464"></path><path d="M6.003 5.125a4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Documentazione Più Intelligente</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">L&#x27;AI Scribe utilizza i dati dei tracciatori per generare note più ricche e contestuali.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-vibrant/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chart-column h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16"></path><path d="M18 17V9"></path><path d="M13 17V5"></path><path d="M8 17v-3"></path></svg>Copertura Completa dei Parametri</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Monitoraggio della Salute Completo</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Traccia oltre 70 parametri di salute — dai segni vitali allo stile di vita — tutti unificati nell&#x27;EHR del paziente, con dati che affluiscono da pazienti, operatori e dispositivi per supportare l&#x27;assistenza continua.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Segni Vitali e Dati Fisiologici</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Monitora pressione sanguigna, frequenza cardiaca, SpO₂, peso, temperatura e altro con sincronizzazione in tempo reale da dispositivi o inserimento manuale.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-activity h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Parametri per Condizioni Croniche</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Traccia glucosio, frequenza respiratoria e altri marcatori critici per la gestione di diabete, ipertensione, BPCO e condizioni cardiache.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-trending-up h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 7h6v6"></path><path d="m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Metriche di Fitness e Benessere</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Segui attività, sonno, composizione corporea, cicli mestruali, nutrizione e umore per supportare l&#x27;assistenza preventiva e olistica.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-database h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Indicatori Specifici per Specialità</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Abilita il giusto sottoinsieme di tracciatori per ogni specialità — dalla funzionalità renale ed epatica alla salute delle donne — adattato alle esigenze del paziente.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Dashboard di monitoraggio sanitario completo" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fcomplete-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fcomplete-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fcomplete-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Tracciatori sanitari integrati nell&#x27;assistenza clinica quotidiana" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fhealth-trackers-in-everyday-care.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fhealth-trackers-in-everyday-care.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fhealth-trackers-in-everyday-care.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-success/20 text-green-success px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-green-success/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-stethoscope h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11 2v2"></path><path d="M5 2v2"></path><path d="M5 3H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1"></path><path d="M8 15a6 6 0 0 0 12 0v-3"></path><circle cx="20" cy="10" r="2"></circle></svg>Integrazione nell&#x27;Assistenza Quotidiana</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Tracciatori Sanitari nell&#x27;Assistenza Quotidiana</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">I Tracciatori Sanitari sono più che semplici punti dati — costituiscono la spina dorsale dell&#x27;assistenza continua all&#x27;interno della Pratica Virtuale. Dal supporto ai piani di Monitoraggio Remoto dei Pazienti all&#x27;assistenza agli operatori durante le consulenze, garantiscono che le informazioni sulla salute del paziente siano sempre utilizzabili.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Base per RPM</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Soglie personalizzate e avvisi nei piani di Monitoraggio Remoto dei Pazienti sono costruiti direttamente sui dati dei tracciatori.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-stethoscope h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11 2v2"></path><path d="M5 2v2"></path><path d="M5 3H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1"></path><path d="M8 15a6 6 0 0 0 12 0v-3"></path><circle cx="20" cy="10" r="2"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Contesto per Consulenze</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Gli operatori possono esaminare le tendenze sanitarie longitudinali durante gli incontri, aggiungere nuove misurazioni e utilizzare le informazioni per guidare le decisioni terapeutiche.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Monitoraggio Basato su Team</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Assegna responsabilità di monitoraggio a un team di operatori in modo che i dati del paziente non passino mai inosservati.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-brain h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 18V5"></path><path d="M15 13a4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3-4 4.17 4.17 0 0 1-3 4"></path><path d="M17.598 6.5A3 3 0 1 0 12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.598 1.5"></path><path d="M17.997 5.125a4 4 0 0 1 2.526 5.77"></path><path d="M18 18a4 4 0 0 0 2-7.464"></path><path d="M19.967 17.483A4 4 0 1 1 12 18a4 4 0 1 1-7.967-.517"></path><path d="M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-2-7.464"></path><path d="M6.003 5.125a4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Documentazione Più Intelligente</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">I dati dei tracciatori sono archiviati nell&#x27;EHR e referenziati da strumenti come l&#x27;AI Scribe, aiutando gli operatori a creare note accurate e ricche di contesto.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-teal-primary/20 text-teal-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-teal-primary/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg>Connettività Dispositivi</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Ampia Compatibilità dei Dispositivi</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Sincronizza i dati sanitari da più fonti — dispositivi abilitati Bluetooth, indossabili connessi, piattaforme sanitarie come Apple Health e Google Health Connect e persino sistemi di misurazione basati su IA. Tutti i dati confluiscono nell&#x27;EHR, pronti per l&#x27;uso nei piani di assistenza e nelle consulenze.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-link h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Integrazione Dispositivi di Terze Parti</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Funziona con un&#x27;ampia gamma di monitor abilitati Bluetooth e dispositivi indossabili.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-award h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526"></path><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Dispositivi Consumer e di Grado Clinico</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Compatibile sia con tracciatori sanitari quotidiani che con apparecchiature mediche validate.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Integrazioni Piattaforme Sanitarie</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">I pazienti possono collegare i loro account Apple Health (iOS) o Google Health Connect (Android) per condividere i parametri supportati.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-database h-6 w-6 text-teal-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Accesso EHR Unificato</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">I dati sincronizzati sono archiviati in modo sicuro nella cartella sanitaria del paziente e visibili agli operatori ovunque necessario.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Vari dispositivi di monitoraggio sanitario e indossabili" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fextensive-device-compatibility.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fextensive-device-compatibility.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fextensive-device-compatibility.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Specialisti medici che utilizzano strumenti di monitoraggio specializzati" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Ftailored-for-real-world-care.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Ftailored-for-real-world-care.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Ftailored-for-real-world-care.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-purple-accent/20 text-purple-accent px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-purple-accent/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-stethoscope h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11 2v2"></path><path d="M5 2v2"></path><path d="M5 3H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1"></path><path d="M8 15a6 6 0 0 0 12 0v-3"></path><circle cx="20" cy="10" r="2"></circle></svg>Ottimizzazione per Specialità</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Su Misura per l&#x27;Assistenza nel Mondo Reale</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">I Tracciatori Sanitari si adattano al modo in cui le diverse discipline forniscono assistenza — dalla gestione delle condizioni a lungo termine al supporto del recupero e della salute preventiva.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Gestione delle Cure Croniche</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Tracciamento continuo di glucosio, pressione sanguigna, frequenza respiratoria e altri marcatori per condizioni come diabete, ipertensione e BPCO.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Monitoraggio Post-Chirurgico e a Breve Termine</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Traccia segni vitali e sintomi durante i periodi di recupero, con avvisi per interventi precoci.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-trending-up h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 7h6v6"></path><path d="m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Supporto Preventivo e dello Stile di Vita</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Monitora attività, sonno, nutrizione e umore per guidare piani di benessere e assistenza preventiva.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-stethoscope h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11 2v2"></path><path d="M5 2v2"></path><path d="M5 3H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1"></path><path d="M8 15a6 6 0 0 0 12 0v-3"></path><circle cx="20" cy="10" r="2"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Approfondimenti Pronti per le Consulenze</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Gli operatori possono esaminare i dati sanitari longitudinali durante gli incontri per informare i passi successivi.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-orange-startup/20 text-orange-startup px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-orange-startup/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg>Collaborazione con i Pazienti</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Monitoraggio della Salute Condiviso</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">I Tracciatori Sanitari trasformano i pazienti in partner attivi nella propria cura. Registrando dati, sincronizzando dispositivi e monitorando i progressi nell&#x27;app per pazienti, gli individui rimangono coinvolti — mentre gli operatori acquisiscono il contesto per guidarli in modo più efficace.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target h-6 w-6 text-orange-startup flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Imposta e Traccia Obiettivi Insieme</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Operatori e pazienti concordano su obiettivi di salute e misurano i progressi in modo collaborativo.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-6 w-6 text-orange-startup flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Visibilità Continua</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">I pazienti condividono aggiornamenti in tempo reale, così gli operatori possono vedere le tendenze senza aspettare la prossima visita.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-orange-startup flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Cicli di Feedback Significativi</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Gli operatori possono commentare i progressi, adeguare i piani e celebrare i traguardi per mantenere motivati i pazienti.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-6 w-6 text-orange-startup flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Maggiore Coinvolgimento</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">I pazienti sentono di possedere i propri dati, favorendo l&#x27;adesione e la partecipazione a lungo termine nei piani di assistenza.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Operatore sanitario e paziente che collaborano sul monitoraggio della salute" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fshared-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fshared-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_trackers%2Fshared-health-monitoring.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Virtual Practice platform is delivering next-generation medical care. As a multidisciplinary team, we find it powerful and intuitive for organizing patient cases, with clear medical records that support precise documentation and effective care.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Georgios Leon - Metabolic Specialist</p><p class="text-gray-600">Precision Medicine Startup, Greece</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->It&#x27;s been an easy, practical and reliable tool to manage my medical records. It has many useful tools that had saved me not only time but also lives because I can access patient files from my phone wherever I am.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Nery Orozco</p><p class="text-gray-600">Vascular Surgeon, Guatemala</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What are Health Trackers in the Virtual Practice?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Health Trackers are a library of 70+ parameters — from vitals and labs to lifestyle metrics — that patients and providers can record. All data is stored inside the patient's electronic health record (EHR)."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do Health Trackers improve care for providers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"They provide a continuous view of patient health between visits, power Remote Patient Monitoring care plans, and make longitudinal trends visible during consultations."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can patients log their own health data?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can log readings manually through the portal or mobile app, as well as sync data from devices and health apps."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which devices and health apps are supported?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Health Trackers connect with Bluetooth-enabled monitors, wearables, and popular platforms like Apple Health (iOS) and Google Health Connect (Android)."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers add measurements during visits?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Absolutely. Providers can add vitals or other measurements taken during in-person or telehealth consultations, ensuring the EHR is always up to date."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do Health Trackers support Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Tracker data is the foundation of RPM care plans. Providers can set personalized thresholds, assign monitoring teams, and receive alerts when readings fall outside the safe range."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Are patients actively involved with Health Trackers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Patients can view their own data, track progress toward goals, and collaborate with providers through shared monitoring and feedback loops."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do Health Trackers integrate with AI features?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Tracker data in the EHR provides context for AI Scribe, helping providers generate richer, more accurate consultation notes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can clinics customize which trackers are available?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Admins choose which subset of the 70+ trackers is relevant for their practice or individual patients."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is tracker data secure and compliant?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. All data is stored securely within the EHR and managed under strict healthcare privacy and security standards."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What are Health Trackers in the Virtual Practice?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What are Health Trackers in the Virtual Practice?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="How do Health Trackers improve care for providers?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">How do Health Trackers improve care for providers?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Can patients log their own health data?" class="w-full tex